entry.title: Satellite Images of Crimea Air Base Indicate Explosions Destroyed Russian Jets
entry.content: Before-and-after photographs of the facility contradict Russia’s official account that no planes were lost in the blasts. Ukraine said nine combat aircraft were destroyed.

entry.title: China's Bursting Housing Bubble Compounds Its Economic Woes
entry.content: Home sales and prices are dropping in many cities across the country after rising for years, and the damage is spreading. “We’ve never seen a property market slowdown of this size and severity.”

entry.title: The Dangerous Mission to Sneak Sacks of Cash in Western Aid Into Myanmar
entry.content: Major organizations have limited access since last year’s military coup, leaving members of smaller groups to sneak in aid money via Thailand.
